## 01. Executive Summary

**ManSula BOS** (Business Operating System) is a privacy-first, offline-capable Point of Sale (POS) and Business Management Progressive Web Application (PWA). It targets retail shops, pop-up stores, cafes, and small-to-medium enterprises (SMEs) who require a fast, reliable billing system that works without a permanent internet connection.

The application runs entirely in the browser using React.js and IndexedDB. All business data — products, inventory, orders, customers, financial history — is stored locally on the merchant's device. No user data is ever transmitted to external servers.

**Core Differentiators:**
- 100% Offline-First: Functions without internet after first load.
- Zero Cloud Subscriptions: No SaaS fees, no monthly billing.
- Privacy by Architecture: No external data transmission.
- Hardware-Agnostic: Runs on any smartphone, tablet, or PC browser.
- Dynamic UPI Integration: Generates exact-amount QR codes on the fly.

