## 05. User Flows

### 5.1 First-Time Onboarding
```
App Launch
    ↓
Splash Screen (Welcome animation)
    ↓
Privacy & Terms Agreement (Must accept to proceed)
    ↓
Theme Selection (Light / Dark)
    ↓
Home Dashboard
    ↓
Business Profile Setup Spotlight (shown if 'mn-business.name' is empty)
```

### 5.2 Standard Checkout Flow
```
POS Screen
    ↓
Browse Product Grid → Tap to Add / Scan Barcode / Custom Quick-Add
    ↓
[If product has Variants] → Variant Selection Modal
    ↓
Cart builds up with items
    ↓
Apply Discount (flat amount)
    ↓
Apply Delivery Charge
    ↓
Review Totals (Subtotal + Tax - Discount + Delivery = Total)
    ↓
Select Payment Mode [Cash / UPI / Card / Udhaar / Split]
    ↓
[If UPI] → Dynamic QR code generated from UPI ID + amount
    ↓
Confirm Checkout
    ↓
Order saved to IndexedDB orders store
Inventory stock deducted for all items
    ↓
Success Modal shown (order summary, total, payment mode)
    ↓
Cart cleared → ready for next order
```

### 5.3 Backup Flow
```
Home → More Tools → Backup & Restore
    ↓
Status Card shows: Last backup date + System Secure / Action Required
    ↓
Tap "Download" → exportUltimateBackup()
    ↓
All IndexedDB stores fetched + localStorage mn- keys fetched
    ↓
JSON blob serialized → Saved as MansulaBOS_FullBackup_DD-MM-YYYY.msbos
    ↓
mn-last-backup-date updated in localStorage
    ↓
Backup complete toast shown
```

### 5.4 App Update Flow
```
App loads in background (PWA Service Worker running)
    ↓
Vite PWA detects new version deployed to hosting
    ↓
'needRefresh' becomes true → ReloadPrompt renders
    ↓
Push notification fires: "Update Available"
    ↓
In-app banner appears at bottom: "New ManSula BOS update available"
    ↓
User taps "Update Now"
    ↓
updateServiceWorker(true) called → page reloads with new version
```

