**App Update:**
```json
{
  "title": "Update Available",
  "body": "A new version of ManSula BOS is ready! Tap here to open and update.",
  "tag": "app-update"
}
```

### 14.3 Notification Permission Flow
1. User navigates to Settings (Home) → App Permissions → Notifications → "Allow".
2. Or: User opens Backup & Restore → Push Notifications → "Enable".
3. Both call `Notification.requestPermission()` directly in the click handler.
4. Callback method used to support legacy Safari + modern Promise API simultaneously.
5. Permission state read back via `Notification.permission` (`'granted'`, `'denied'`, `'default'`).

