## 21. Risks & Mitigation

| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|
| Device loss / theft | High | Weekly backup push notifications; `.msbos` export to cloud storage |
| Browser clears IndexedDB | Medium | `navigator.storage.persist()` called on boot to mark DB as persistent |
| Storage quota exceeded | Medium | Periodic monitoring via `navigator.storage.estimate()`; warn at 90% |
| iOS Safari notification limitations | Medium | Direct `Notification.requestPermission()` call in click handler (not wrapped in async chain) |
| Breaking schema changes | Medium | `version` field in backup format enables structured migration |

